{
  "page": "House Lannister of Darry",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Lannister of Darry</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Lannister_of_Darry.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Lannister of Darry.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7a/House_Lannister_of_Darry.svg/250px-House_Lannister_of_Darry.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7a/House_Lannister_of_Darry.svg/375px-House_Lannister_of_Darry.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7a/House_Lannister_of_Darry.svg/500px-House_Lannister_of_Darry.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nQuarterly clockwise, a gold lion on a crimson field; a black plowman on a brown field<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup><br /><i>(Quarterly, first and third gules, a lion or, second and fourth brunâtre, a plowman sable)</i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Seat</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Darry\" title=\"Darry\">Darry</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nLady <a href=\"/index.php/Amerei_Frey\" title=\"Amerei Frey\">Amerei Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Darry\" title=\"Lord of Darry\">Lady of Darry</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Baelish\" title=\"House Baelish\">House Baelish</a> (ADWD)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Founder</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Lancel_Lannister\" title=\"Lancel Lannister\">Lancel Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Founded</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Lannister of Darry</b> is a new noble house from <a href=\"/index.php/Darry\" title=\"Darry\">Castle Darry</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>, and a cadet branch of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>. The new houses's sigil is the Lion of Lannister, gold on red, quartered with the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\">Darry</a> plowman.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#House_Lannister_of_Darry_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Lannister of Darry at the end of the third century</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Household\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Household</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Lannister_of_Darry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Lannister_of_Darry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lancel_Lannister\" title=\"Lancel Lannister\">Lancel Lannister</a> is granted <a href=\"/index.php/Darry\" title=\"Darry\">Castle Darry</a> and its lands after the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>, as <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\">House Darry</a>'s child lord, <a href=\"/index.php/Lyman_Darry\" title=\"Lyman Darry\">Lyman Darry</a>, died during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Lannister_of_Darry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lancel is betrothed to <a href=\"/index.php/Amerei_Frey\" title=\"Amerei Frey\">Amerei Frey</a>, daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Mariya_Darry\" title=\"Mariya Darry\">Mariya Darry</a>, per the alliance between <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a>. Mariya's younger sister, <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Darry\" title=\"Jeyne Darry\">Jeyne Darry</a>, is dismayed that the lordship was granted to Lancel rather than one of her own young sons. Despite the house's banners combining the sigils of Lannister and Darry, an idea of <a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a>, the house functions more as a branch of the Freys due to their numbers and Lancel's disinterest in his lordly duties.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Harwyn_Plumm\" title=\"Harwyn Plumm\">Harwyn Plumm</a> leads some men to root out outlaws on the Darry lands, to little effect.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Later <a href=\"/index.php/Lyle_Crakehall\" title=\"Lyle Crakehall\">Lyle Crakehall</a>, charmed by Amerei, leaves <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> to conclude the campaign.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord Lancel renounces both lordship and his unconsummated marriage to join the <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Lannister_of_Darry_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Lannister of Darry at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Lannister_of_Darry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Lannister of Darry at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Lannisters of Darry during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lancel_Lannister\" title=\"Lancel Lannister\">Lancel Lannister</a>, the new Lord of Darry, son of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a>. Forsook lands, title and wife to join the <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a>.\n<ul><li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Amerei_Frey\" title=\"Amerei Frey\">Amerei Frey</a>, called \"Gatehouse Ami\", his wife.</li></ul></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Household\">Household</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Lannister_of_Darry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Household\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Mariya_Darry\" title=\"Mariya Darry\">Mariya Darry</a>, Lady Amerei's mother.\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Marissa_Frey\" title=\"Marissa Frey\">Marissa Frey</a>, Lady Amerei's sister and Lady Mariya's daughter, a maid of three-and-ten.</li></ul></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Danwell_Frey\" title=\"Danwell Frey\">Danwell Frey</a>, Lady Amerei's uncle.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arwood_Frey\" title=\"Arwood Frey\">Arwood Frey</a>, Lady Amerei's cousin.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Leslyn_Haigh\" title=\"Leslyn Haigh\">Leslyn Haigh</a>, a half-uncle of Lady Amerei's, and his sons Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harys_Haigh\" title=\"Harys Haigh\">Harys</a>, and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_Haigh\" title=\"Donnel Haigh\">Donnel</a>, household knights all</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Ottomore\" title=\"Ottomore\">Ottomore</a>, counselor and healer.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harwyn_Plumm\" title=\"Harwyn Plumm\">Harwyn Plumm</a>, called \"Hardstone\", commander of the Darry garrison.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Lannister_of_Darry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">In <a href=\"/index.php/Westerosi\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Westerosi\">Westerosi</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Heraldry\" title=\"Heraldry\">heraldry</a>, the quarters are listed clockwise rather than the traditional 1-2/3-4 order.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Lannister_of_Darry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Alayne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Alayne I (The Winds of Winter)\">Alayne I</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">The Mystery Knight: The Graphic Novel</a></i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">4.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\">4.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-3\">4.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_30\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 30\">Chapter 30</a>, Jaime IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_65\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 65\">Chapter 65</a>, Sansa VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_44\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 44\">Chapter 44</a>, Jaime VII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;paddi